bonsaimind.org
==============

This is the source code for the [bonsaimind.org](https://www.bonsaimind.org)
website. It is a Markdown document which is converted to HTML with
Pandoc](https://pandoc.org/).


License
=======

The build script (`build.sh`), the Lua filter (`filter.lua`) and the template
file (`index.template`) can be considered to be under CC0 or Public Domain.

The index file (`index.markdown`) has to be considered "All Rights Reserved",
with the exception of cloning this repository, and being edited for the purpose
of merging these changes back.

The avatar (`avatar.png`) and logo (`logo.svg`) have to be considered
"All Rights Reserved" with the exception of cloning this repository. However,
modifications or reuse of these two files are not allowed.

The icons (`icons.svg`) is a SVG sprite with icons from [Font Awesome](https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome), see the attached license file for further details.


Build
=====

Run the build script to generate the website.
